    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka will be dragged to the bottom and the President will leave the country",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "BBC reports that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has left for Mal\u00e9, the capital of the Maldives in an air force jet. The news service reports the information.",
        "The news service reports that the 73-year-old Gotabaya Rajapaksa has reached the capital city of Male today at around 3:00 am Maldives time.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is going to resign from his position today and before that he has gone to Maldives.",
        "The President has signed his resignation letter. It was reported earlier that he had planned to leave the country after that."
      ],
